---
---

<section id="pricing" class="py-32 relative bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
            <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">透明且靈活的投資方案</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-light">無隱藏費用，為您的企業量身打造最合適的 AI SEO 自動化引擎。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto items-center">
            
            <!-- Tier 1 -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-brand-300 transition-colors">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">初階方案</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">適合剛起步的新創品牌或在地商家</p>
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">HK$3,800</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">/ 年</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-sm text-slate-600 font-light">
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>基礎 AI 關鍵字分析</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>每月 2 篇 AI 優化文章</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>基礎技術 SEO 審查</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>季度成效報告</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#contact" class="block w-full py-3 px-6 text-center rounded-full text-slate-700 font-bold border-2 border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-900 hover:text-slate-900 transition-all">
                    立即預約
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Tier 2 (Most Popular) -->
            <div class="glass-card p-10 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden bg-white border-2 border-slate-900 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-900/10 transform md:-translate-y-4">
                <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-400 via-blue-500 to-indigo-500"></div>
                <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 bg-slate-900 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">最受歡迎</div>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">專業方案</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">適合追求快速成長的中小企業 B2B</p>
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900">HK$9,800</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">/ 年</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-sm text-slate-700 font-light">
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>深度競爭者與長尾關鍵字洞察</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>每月 8 篇高權重 (E-E-A-T) 文章</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>全面技術 SEO (速度與 Schema)</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>每月即時監測與優化報告</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>基本外部連結建置</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#contact" class="block w-full py-4 px-6 text-center rounded-full bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white font-bold transition-all shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/20 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                    立即預約
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Tier 3 -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-brand-300 transition-colors">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">企業方案</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">適合大型機構與跨國市場佈局</p>
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">HK$48,000</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">/ 年</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-sm text-slate-600 font-light">
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>全自動化 AI 行銷引擎串接</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>無上限 AI 內容生成與多語系</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>進階數位公關與高 DA 連結</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>專屬客戶經理與 CRM 整合</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>API 串接與客製化控制台</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#contact" class="block w-full py-3 px-6 text-center rounded-full text-slate-700 font-bold border-2 border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-900 hover:text-slate-900 transition-all">
                    聯絡專員
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>